Package eu.mihosoft.freerouting.interactive

Class ActivityReplayFileScope

java.lang.Object
eu.mihosoft.freerouting.interactive.ActivityReplayFileScope
public abstract class ActivityReplayFileScope extends Object
Enumeration class defining scopes in a logfile, Each Object of the class must implement the read_scope method.
